DESCRIPTION;LANGUAGE=en-US:Weekly Monday event using bare timestamps (no offset). Hugo interprets these in the site timezone (Europe/Zurich). DTSTART should be TZID=Europe/Zurich:20260315T180000. Compare with test_recurring_until_future which uses the same date/time but icaltimezone override.
